            "Masterwork Rapier"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "summary_update": {
    "last_scene": [
      "Artie encountered the Level 28 Paladin Vane outside the Mayor's office, who challenged him to a duel to test his 'Anomaly' status.",
      "By bluffing that his 1 HP was actually a 'Perfect Guard' reflection build, Artie convinced the high-level warrior to stand down.",
      "Shaken but successful, Artie began heading toward the Low-Level Crypts to find evasion gear before his bluff is exposed."
    ],
    "key_events": [
      "Artie received a formal quest update for 'The Mayor’s Cut' with a 24-hour deadline.",
      "Vane, a Level 28 Sun-Blessed Paladin, intercepted Artie and initiated a Duel Request.",
      "Artie successfully bluffed that his 1 HP is a 'Perfect Guard' mechanic that reflects 200% damage.",
      "Vane withdrew his challenge but promised to monitor Artie for 'System instability'.",
      "Artie's stamina and hunger reached critical levels (14 and 10 respectively).",
      "Fizz suggested the Low-Level Crypts as a source for 'Coward’s Gear' to bolster Artie's survival."
    ],
    "must_stay_true": [
      "milestone: vane_first_encounter = DONE",
      "milestone: perfect_guard_bluff_established = DONE",
      "Artie has 1 HP and 100% Crit Rate.",
      "Artie is carrying the Participation Trophy in his left hand (Soul-bound, +500% aggro).",
      "Vane is a Level 28 Paladin and a member of the Order of the Golden Ratio.",
      "Artie has 24 hours to pay the 500-gold Variance Tax.",
      "Artie's Super-Mega-Ultra-Crit is on a 24-hour cooldown."
    ],
    "chapter_so_far_add": [
      "Artie successfully bluffed the Paladin Vane into believing he possesses a 'Perfect Guard' reflection build.",
      "Vane has been established as a high-level antagonist who views Artie as a potential System virus."
    ]
  },
  "threads_touched": [
    "THREAD_VANE_RIVALRY",
    "THREAD_CRIT_EXPLOIT"
  ],
  "world_updates": {
    "cast_present_ids": [
      "CHAR_ARTIE",
      "CHAR_VANE"
    ],
    "location": "Oakhaven - Hallway and Streets",
    "recent_facts": [
      "Artie bluffed Vane into believing he has a reflection build.",
      "Vane is a Level 28 Paladin from the Order of the Golden Ratio.",
      "Artie is heading to the Low-Level Crypts to farm evasion gear."
    ]
  }
}

